precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a HEADQUARTERS
AGREEMENT between Canada and the COMMISSION FOR ENVIRONMENTAL COOPERATION,
or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing other officials to
sign the Agreement on behalf of the Government of Canada.
